{"word":"ἅρπαξ","slug":"ἅρπαξ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἅρπαξ</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἁρπάζω'><el>ἁρπάζω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>rapacious</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>rapax</el>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>as <a href='S:Substantive'>Subst.</a>,<p/></div><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><el>ἅρπαξ</el>, <i>rapine</i>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><el>ἅρπαξ</el>, <i>a robber, plunderer</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}